{
  "texts": [
    "In P4, participants may see the NDA with top 5%, 10%, or 20% of the important words highlighted (Fig. 13), and in P5, the top 3 most influential labeled train examples with Input×Gradient highlights incorporatedparticipants should not have to fully review three different NDAs to quickly verify if the AI's guess is correct.",
    "Appendix D.5 provides more info.",
    "For each study, we aim for 80 examples for each of the three labels.",
    "We gather 35-40 participant responses per study, with each participant annotating up to 6 samples.",
    "We collect 1108 annotations across all conditions."
  ]
}